Why Our Prices are Lower



WE OFFER DISCOUNTS based on the total quantity of all the items on your order.
OUR COMPETITORS only offer discounts on orders of dozens or full cases of one size and color.
SINCE MOST ORDERS are comprised of multiple colors and sizes in each style, you will find the cost of your total order will be less at T-Shirt Wholesaler.









  
 
