Quantity discounts
The more you order the cheaper it gets!
Our willingness to satisfy our customers goes by our volume discounts system.
It's really simple, you start benefiting 15% off on your twelfth ordered item and 25% off at your thirty sixth item.
How do I benefit from these discounts?
You do not have to rely solely on the same model to get those discounts. You can mix and match any models, sizes, colors and brands and yet benefit from those discounted volume prices in your final cart. So you can order 5 t-shirts, 5 pairs of sweatpants and three hats then you're at 15% off on everything.
So you can already see the importance of group orders; tell your friends, suppliers, coworkers and family members about this system and why not place an order all together? Then you all benefit from our volume discounts. Businesses can also group different lines and order their garment needs at once!
Buy our blank apparel






