h is 99/1 Cotton/Poly. Lilac, Midnight, Sunset, Russet, Blackberry, Tweed, Safety, neon and all Heather colors are 50/50 Cotton/Poly). Note: Gildan labels this item "heavy cotton", however we feel that most customers would describe it as lightweight. Sizes: S-5XLMatching Item(s):See the Gildan Youth Lightweight 100% Cotton T-ShirtSee the Gildan Ladie's Lightweight 100% Cotton T-ShirtSee the Gildan Lightweight Cotton Toddler T-ShirtANTIQU JADE DOMEANTIQU JADE DOMEANTIQUE CHERRY REDANTIQUE CHERRY REDANTIQUE IRISH GREENANTIQUE IRISH GREENANTIQUE ORANGEANTIQUE ORANGEANTIQUE SAPPHIREANTIQUE SAPPHIREASHASHAZALEAAZALEABERRYBERRYBLACKBLACKBLACKBERRYBLACKBERRYBROWN SAVANABROWN SAVANACARDINALCARDINALCAROLINA BLUECAROLINA BLUECHARCOALCHARCOALCOBALTCOBALTCORAL SILKCORAL SILKCORNSILKCORNSILKDAISYDAISYDARK CHOCOLATEDARK CHOCOLATEDARK HEATHERDARK HEATHERELECTRIC GREENELECTRIC GREENFOREST GREENFOREST GREENGARNETGARNETGOLDGOLDGRAPHITE HEATHERGRAPHITE HEATHERGRAVELGRAVELHEATHER MILITARY GREENHEATHER MILITARY GREENHEATHER REDHEATHER REDHEATHER SAPPHIREHEATHER SAPPHIREHELICONIAHELICONIAHTHR RDNT ORCHIDHTHR RDNT ORCHIDICE GREYICE GREYINDIGO BLUEINDIGO BLUEIRISH GREENIRISH GREENKIWIKIWILIGHT BLUELIGHT BLUELIGHT PINKLIGHT PINKLILACLILACLIMELIMEMAROONMAROONMIDNIGHTMIDNIGHTMILITARY GREENMILITARY GREENMINT GREENMINT GREENNATURALNATURALNAVYNAVYNEON BLUENEON BLUENEON GREENNEON GREENOLD GOLDOLD GOLDORANGEORANGEPURPLEPURPLEREDREDROYALROYALRUSSETRUSSETSAFETY GREENSAFETY GREENSAFETY ORANGESAFETY ORANGESAFETY PINKSAFETY PINKSANDSANDSAPPHIRESAPPHIRESKYSKYSPORT GREYSPORT GREYSUNSETSUNSETTENNESSEE ORANGETENNESSEE ORANGETEXAS ORANGETEXAS ORANGETROPICAL BLUETROPICAL BLUETURF GREENTURF GREENTWEEDTWEEDVIOLETVIOLETWHITEWHITEYELLOW HAZEYELLOW HAZEColors are approximationsSimilar ProductsGildan Lightweight 100% Cotton T-Shirt | Next Level Ladie's Ideal V-Neck Tee | Jerzees 50/50 Jersey Knit Polo Shirt | Fruit of the Loom 100% Cotton T-Shirt | Gildan Ladie's Lightweight 100% Cotton T-Shirt | Gildan Youth Ligh